epiphany-browser (3.2.0-2) experimental; urgency=low

  [ Michael Biebl ]
  * debian/control.in:
    - Drop Build-Depends on libdbus-glib-1-dev (ported to GDBus).
    - Drop Build-Depends on libstartup-notification0-dev.
    - Drop Build-Depends on network-manager-dev.
  * debian/rules:
    - Drop obsolete --enable-network-manager configure flag. NetworkManager
      support is enabled unconditionally. As dbus is used to to access
      NetworkManager, this does not add a hard dependency.

  [ Gustavo Noronha Silva ]
  * debian/control.in:
  - Rename the gir package acknoledging the file name change

 -- Gustavo Noronha Silva <kov@debian.org>  Sun, 16 Oct 2011 22:52:15 -0200

epiphany-browser (3.2.0-1) experimental; urgency=low

  * New upstream release
  * debian/control.in:
  - bump build dependencies on webkitgtk to 1.6.1 and glib to 2.29.10
  - add build dependency on libnotify-dev >= 0.5.1
  * debian/watch:
  - watch for .tar.xz files
  * debian/patches/00_epiphany-browser.patch:
  - refreshed
  * debian/patches/11_browse_to.patch:
  - applied upstream
  * debian/patches/03_dbus.patch:
  - Epiphany no longer uses dbus directly, but relies on GtkApplication
    for the functionality, which makes this patch obsolete
  * debian/patches/02_format-security.patch:
  - added; fix -Wformat-security build errors

 -- Gustavo Noronha Silva <kov@debian.org>  Sun, 16 Oct 2011 13:55:33 -0200

epiphany-browser (3.0.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * debian/control.in:
    - Bump Build-Depends on libwebkitgtk-3.0-dev to (>= 1.4.2).
    - Remove Build-Depends on gir1.2-gtk-3.0 and let libgtk-3-dev pull that
      dependency in. Bump Build-Depends on libgtk-3-dev to (>= 3.0.8-1~)
      accordingly.
  * Disable seed support on mips. Should be re-enabled when #633730 is fixed.
  * Upload to unstable. Remove check-dist.mk include.
  * debian/rules: Remove obsolete configure options.

 -- Michael Biebl <biebl@debian.org>  Fri, 22 Jul 2011 01:26:08 +0200

epiphany-browser (3.0.3-1) experimental; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * debian/watch:
    - Don't run uupdate.
    - Switch to .bz2 tarballs.
  * Refresh debian/patches/03_dbus.patch.
  * debian/control.in:
    - Bump Build-Depends on libsoup-gnome2.4-dev to (>= 2.33.1).
    - Bump Standards-Version to 3.9.2. No further changes.
    - Remove old Conflicts and Replaces which are no longer necessary.

